# Afenda Coding Session (always on)

**Skill (full workflow):** [`.cursor/skills/afenda-coding-session/SKILL.md`](../skills/afenda-coding-session/SKILL.md) — invoke with `/afenda-coding-session` for §0–§11 detail, hard stops, and gate matrix ([VERIFICATION.md](../skills/afenda-coding-session/VERIFICATION.md)).

**Catalog:** [`.cursor/skills/README.md`](../skills/README.md) · **Routing:** [`.cursor/rules/skills-routing.mdc`](skills-routing.mdc)

## Every coding turn

1. **Announce:** `I'm using afenda-coding-session — stating the execution contract before edits.`
2. **Before any Write/StrReplace:** Post **Phase 0** (all six lines) per skill §0 — do not edit until done.
3. **Implement:** Follow skill §3–§10; hard stops at skill §0.1.
4. **Before ending turn:** Post **Completion Report** per skill §11 (drift-prevention table + gate evidence).

If upstream contract is missing: **stop and report** — no local registries, tokens, permissions, or tenant resolvers.

**PAS foundation work:** read [`foundation-delivery-authority.md`](../../docs/architecture/foundation-delivery-authority.md) and derive Phase 0 from registry + `docs/PAS/slice/` handoffs.

Implementer agents: attach [`coding-consistency-bundle`](../skills/coding-consistency-bundle/SKILL.md) — bundle preflight runs **before** Phase 0.
